## Commands
- Install deps: `uv sync` (and `uv sync --dev`)
- Tests: `uv run pytest` (never call pytest directly)
- Lint: `uv run ruff check .`; Format: `uv run ruff format .`;

## Practices
- Use markers (`slow`, `integration`) and coverage for both packages
- Keep tests organized and type-safe; prefer parametrized tests where useful

